The air is my favorite place to be these days and I’m so excited to be debuting a new aerial act at @adelewolfproductions 11th Annual NYE Bash! 🪩 I can hardly stand to keep it under wraps but I want to surprise you! 🥰 I’ll be doing my Champagne Dream act as well! ✨ It’s become tradition to take a champagne bath in my coupe every year since its debut in 2018!🍾The lineup is stacked with amazing talent and VIP Tables are already sold out! 🔥Only a few front row seats remain so get them while you can to ring in NYE in the best way possible! 

📷: @dsbittle at Adèle Wolf’s Moonlight Revue in Aug. 2022

@adelewolfproductions 11th Annual NYE Bash is quickly approaching and the holidays are even closer! ✨ Treat someone special to a truly out of this world experience this New Year’s Eve! 🪩 Our award-winning cast will deliver sights never before seen in Oklahoma including performances by special guest @noemi_fallu from Vegas! 🎉See for yourself why our show is one of Oklahoma’s most anticipated and celebrated NYE events! Seats are going quickly so get them while you can! 🔥

I’ll be so happy to see YOU tomorrow at @adelewolfproductions 11th Annual NYE Bash! 🥰 I’m so excited to ring in the New Year with you, take a dip in my giant champagne coupe, and debut a new aerial act I’ve been hard at work on! 🎉 We have a truly spectacular lineup in store including special guest @noemi_fallu of Cirque du Soleil!🎪 Our show is the hottest ticket in town and we’ve been listed as a top NYE event by @okgazette @_theoklahoman @uncoveringoklahoma @yaydudeokc and @thebestofoklahoma ! Reservations are moving FAST so hurry and get yours to join us for the most dazzling NYE in OKC! ✨

🎥: Footage by @planet.rem at Adèle Wolf’s NYE Bash 2021 Edited by @gadlen_pk

Strutting into 2023 like ✨! I had a blast ringing in the New Year with @adelewolfproductions in OKC. 🎉Starting the year with so many exciting collaborations and shows on the horizon, including my first European tour since 2019 this April-May! 🌍 I was living part time in Europe for a few years pre pandemic and I’m so excited to return! Currently booking, so get in touch if you’d like to see me on your stage! In the meantime, you can catch me at @teaserfestival Jan. 20 in NOLA, @carouselclubburlesque Feb. 3 in Dallas, and Adèle Wolf’s Valentine’s Affair Feb. 11 in OKC! 💖

📷: @dsbittle at Adèle Wolf’s NYE Bash 2022

So excited to bring my award-winning Red Feather Classic act to @hobdallas Main Hall for @carouselclubburlesque this Friday and @adelewolfproductions Valentine’s Affair on Feb. 11th! 💖 VIP tables have sold out and only a few front row seats remain for the Valentine’s Affair in OKC, so get the best seats in the house while you can!🔥

📷: @dsbittle at 2022 @okcburlesque Festival

Can’t wait to perform Slow Love this Saturday at @adelewolfproductions 11th Annual Valentine’s Affair! 💜 I debuted this act the week Prince died and have since performed it around the world. I debuted a new version of the costume at our last show before the pandemic hit in February 2020. I’ve spent many hours rhinestoning and beading since then and I’m so excited to share it with you! 💎

📷: @dsbittle at Adèle Wolf’s Valentine’s Affair Feb. 2020

✨Calling burlesque, circus, vaudeville, cabaret, and variety entertainers of all kinds! ✨Apply now for the 10th Annual Oklahoma City Burlesque Festival happening June 16-17! 🎉 OKCBF is one of the most well respected events on the festival circuit, known for quality over quantity with small showcases of the top performers in the industry, and one of the first U.S. based festivals to pave the way for all paid performance slots. We choose two feature artists from the applicant pool, subsidize a free workshop of the performers choosing, offer teaching opportunities, lots of Midwest hospitality and more! Applications are open until March 19th! Visit our site and apply now to be part of one of the biggest burlesque and variety events worldwide! ✨

Wrapped up my LA trip by meeting @parishilton unexpectedly at LAX! 😮 She was there doing a book signing. My high school bestie and I were obsessed with The Simple Life. She was so personable with everyone, really good energy. She told me I was beautiful and she loved my hair color. 🥰 I told her about my friend and I pretending like we were her and Nicole as kids and she asked who was who. I told her I was Paris and she said,”that’s hot.” 😂 I said we drove my family nuts with that phrase and she said she loved that. It’s great to see her taking control of her narrative and I’m looking forward to reading her book!

Can’t express how happy I am to be back in Europe! 💖For four years, I had a home away from home here. First in Paris and then in Berlin. It was a great chapter of my life and it’s so nice to revisit it. 🥰 It’s a short trip this time so I can get back and take care of business for the 10th Annual @okcburlesque Festival on June 16-17th. Catch me if you can! 💋
